Class Sector

  • java.lang.Object
    • Sector

  • public class Sector
extends java.lang.Object
    A Sector object represents one area which the player can visit in a city. Each Sector object is associated with a SectorType, and a city should contain one Sector of each type.

      • discovered

        private boolean discovered
        Default value is false. A sector is set to discovered if: -the team includes a hero with the map special ability -the team uses a map to reveal all the sectors in the current city -the team has already visited the sector
